Description: # Tyrian Sphinx Theme
        
        A Sphinx theme based on Tyrian (the new unified gentoo.org theme). 
        
        
        - [Installation](#installation)
        - [Configuration](#configuration)
            - [builders](#builders)
            - [sidebar](#sidebar)
            - [navigationlinks_top](#navigationlinks_top)
